I am looking at pathfinding in PathPlannerLib, and have a question. Is it possible to dynamically create obstacles in the field?

I was interested in pathfinding a few weeks ago, and was working on my own AD* implementation before finding that PathPlannerLib already had one. My idea was to avoid obstacles (and automatically go to game pieces) during auto, so I needed to mark field areas as ‚Äúblocked.‚Äù Is this possible in PathPlannerLib? My guess is that PathConstraints might have something to do, but I‚Äôm not sure.

Thank you!
